  "body": "_Part of #9264 keycard sign in epic (mark as checked there, when closing this issue)_\r\n\r\nThe \"Wrong passcode\" indicator should be displayed for 2.2 seconds and disappear (to be replaced with the number of attempts indicator https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/9285), as well as the red background of the dots below it.\r\n\r\nWhen the error appears **the device should vibrate** if possible.\r\n\r\nThe animation of the message should work as follows:\r\n\r\n```\r\nerror-pre-shown: { scale: 1, y: -8, opacity: 0 },\r\nerror-shown: { scale: 1, y: 0, opacity: 1 },\r\nerror-post-shown: { scale: 1, y: 8, opacity: 0 },\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe transition between those states:\r\n\r\n```\r\nduration: 0.4,\r\nease: [0.77, 0, 0.175, 1],\r\n```\r\nVideo:\r\n\r\n<img width=\"375\" alt=\"ыскуут\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/3115606/68083697-c236c780-fe66-11e9-818b-05f9e5815226.gif\">\r\n\r\n\r\nStatic image:\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1153\" alt=\"Untitled5\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/3115606/67676507-9d50d900-f9bc-11e9-97e9-b81577a331c1.png\">\r\n\r\nFigma:\r\nhttps://www.figma.com/file/dEIljL7UPbXgsZUA0Q4qlE5E/Onboarding?node-id=4566%3A12",
