    "body": "@guylouis \r\nI see several issues in current version of the app apart from #9661 in this flow\r\n\r\n## When user is logged out\r\n### 1) Reopening screen from state \"PUK code is required\"  leads to PIN-code screen\r\n If user after exceeding attempts of passcodes tap back and open account from list -> he will see again 6-digit passcode, not sure it is expected. \r\n![ezgif com-video-to-gif (5)](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/80369827-33dc5500-888f-11ea-8bcb-b90563b6aac0.gif)\r\n\r\n### 2) 3 invalid passcode attempts -> valid PUK -> change PIN\r\nIn this case, in the workflow you need to set up a new passcode. \r\nIt is implemented, but not clear from user perspective.\r\nHow it looks now:\r\n![ezgif com-video-to-gif (6)](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/80375195-2d9ea680-8898-11ea-802e-06045ba40bd3.gif)\r\nSo after entering valid PUK code field for some 6-digit code is shown without explanation.\r\n\r\n### 3) 3 invalid passcode attempts -> invalid PUK code -> keycard is frozen\r\nI believe this case is not handled.\r\nSo when user has 0 retries left for entering PUK code, login is freezing with endless spinner.\r\n![ezgif com-video-to-gif (7)](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/80375560-cfbe8e80-8898-11ea-89dc-3e215431aa97.gif)\r\n\r\n## When user is logged in\r\n### 1) Reopening screen from state \"PUK code is required\"  leads to PIN-code screen\r\nIt is same, so state is not preserved\r\n### 2) 3 invalid passcode attempts -> valid PUK -> change PIN\r\nKnown issue #10452 \r\nIn this case change PIN-code is shown behind the \"Signing in flow\"\r\n![ezgif com-video-to-gif (8)](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/80477630-921b3d80-894c-11ea-87f6-f25f3901e472.gif)\r\n### 3) 3 invalid passcode attempts -> invalid PUK code -> keycard is frozen\r\nEndless \r\nAfter 0 retries left for PUK code -> nothing changed, no info that kecard can't be used anymore\r\n![photo_2020-04-28 12 49 36](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/80479312-1ec6fb00-894f-11ea-8e00-e16ef58423cf.jpeg)\r\n\r\n\r\n",
