    "body": "so @hesterbruikman I think we need to define 3 workflows when user is logged in and user is logged out.\r\n#### User is logged in\r\n\r\n- [ ] Reopening screen from state \"PUK code is required\" leads to PIN-code screen\r\n- [ ] 3 invalid passcode attempts -> valid PUK -> change PIN\r\n- [ ] 3 invalid passcode attempts -> invalid PUK code -> keycard is frozen\r\n\r\n#### User is logged out\r\n\r\n- [ ] Reopening screen from state \"PUK code is required\" leads to PIN-code screen\r\n- [ ] 3 invalid passcode attempts -> valid PUK -> change PIN\r\n- [ ] 3 invalid passcode attempts -> invalid PUK code -> keycard is frozen",
